name: Lyn Me
Lore: 'Twi''lek musician whose village hired Boba Fett for protection from slavers. Fell in love with the famous mercenary. Vowed to kill Luke and Han.',
Text: 'Subtracts 1 from deploy cost of Bounty hunters at same site (Boba Fett deploy free). During battle, subtracts X from opponent''s total power, where X = number of your musicians present (+2 if battling Luke or Han, or +4 if both).',
